-- Mediobanca CEO, Chairman set to be re-appointed-source
-- 
-- Thu Jun 19, 2014 01:02PM EDT
-- None



MILAN, June 19 (Reuters) - The current CEO of Mediobanca <MDBI.MI> Alberto Nagel and its Chairman Renato Pagliaro are set to be re-appointed for another three-year mandate, a source close to the Italian investment bank's shareholders said on Thursday.

"There are no doubts," the source said, speaking on condition of anonymity.